metadata.name: It has begun.
metadata.description: It has begun. The choice is yours.  Whether you're a Degen, Collector, extreme sports nut, or adrenaline junkie, by jumping Onboard today, you are now part of the crew.  You are one of the wild ones, the early adaptors, you saw the next big thing and said hell yes, I am in.  This is a game just like life.  You choose how you want it to go.  We are going to give you a hint, you will be the only group that gets this hint because you are F-ing legends and will go down in Onboard history.  Damn, we freaking love you.
